类 RemoteTokenServices

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.springframework.security.oauth2.provider.token.RemoteTokenServices
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    ResourceServerTokenServices

    public class RemoteTokenServices
extends Object
implements ResourceServerTokenServices
    Queries the /check_token endpoint to obtain the contents of an access token. If the endpoint returns a 400 response, this indicates that the token is invalid.
    作者:
    Dave Syer, Luke Taylor

        从接口复制的说明: ResourceServerTokenServices
        Load the credentials for the specified access token.
        指定者:
        loadAuthentication 在接口中 ResourceServerTokenServices
        参数:
        accessToken - The access token value.
